{"tid":887513,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"雞排妹APP釣帥醫男友 羞認被愛人狂攝私密照","createTime":"2018-11-03T03:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T12:10:31.000Z","uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d6cb0aab4f255572c8f30f2940849f38fbfdbe02","tid":887513,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T03:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sp5z63S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsp5z63S.png&h=3d26e7f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《時報周刊》報導，雞排妹在今（ 2018 ）年年初赴日本遊學，為體驗在地生活，也幫直播節目找靈感，決定前往聯誼居酒屋晃晃，但擔心當地素人不願入鏡，這時她腦中閃過「交友軟體」 4 字，正巧手機也有 APP ，就這樣與現任男友相識，「接觸後覺得彼此滿聊得來，就從那時交往到現在。」<br />\n<br />\n雞排妹透露，男友外貌激似吳崢及孔劉，職業則是小兒科醫師，並強調與對方是認真在談戀愛。為與男友溝通雞排妹苦學日文，日語能力在短時間進步神速。此外，為克服遠距離阻礙，她每月飛日本 2 趟，男友也會來台灣見她，雞排妹笑稱對方「非常有耐心，個性又溫柔」，<span style=\"color: red;\">由於男友有攝影興趣，透露對方替她拍了不少私密照，</span>放閃不著痕跡，令粉絲稱羨。"},{"pid":"71f65838b835410fe44610a44fb434f26c96f3c3","tid":887513,"uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T03:43:47.000Z","msg":"]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df38505e4911a729a8dedafd056e0b7efbe72b49","tid":887513,"uid":88691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T03:43:47.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"3a56fb1774b6c078ca4682783abe33b7ddff6c27","tid":887513,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T03:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359cf9d15e0b964b22c209976f5522d45c011705","tid":887513,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T03:47:38.000Z","msg":"性器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3653bf36acfb570430b87bf832625d9e1198aa5d","tid":887513,"uid":159414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T03:51:36.000Z","ms